# FadeCommand.FadeDirection.in

**Case**

A value that represents fading in of the video frames from a requested color.

## Declaration

```swift
case `in`
```

## Enumeration Cases

- **FadeCommand.FadeDirection.out**: A value that represents fading out of the video frames to a requested color.
